 Conclusion

The insights gathered from this survey shaped the tone and features of the app. The prototype avoids aggressive restrictions and instead uses motivational design: positive quotes, soft detox goals, optional challenges, and relaxing alternatives. This aligns with how people said they wanted to reduce screen time â€” without guilt, with kindness.
